│ "thoughts": "### 1. Understanding the Issue\n\nThe LLVM loop vectorizer is crashing with   │
│ an assertion failure in `scalarizeInstruction`. The assertion,                             │
│ `State.TypeAnalysis.inferScalarType(RepRecipe) == Cloned->getType()`, checks for           │
